text: Andrey Kan (born 5 November 1971) is a Belarusian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belarus Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Baranavichy
